              {
                "artifactPos": "",
                "audios": [],
                "desc": "<p>This time, we are looking for a kitten named Lale with black and white fur. If you wish to call for Lale's attention in cat language, you need to say \"Meow, meow meow meow, meow—\" with the tone going downward then upward, before ending on an even higher note.</p>",
                "id": "Additional Information91369",
                "img": "",
                "title": "Lale Version:"
              },
              {
                "artifactPos": "",
                "audios": [],
                "desc": "<p>This time, we are looking for a kitten named Nargis with dark-gray fur. To call for Nargis's attention in cat language, you need to say \"Meow! Meow meow, meow.\" Stress the first meow, and be quick while saying the following meows.</p>",
                "id": "Additional Information86464",
                "img": "",
                "title": "Nargis Version:"
              },
              {
                "artifactPos": "",
                "audios": [],
                "desc": "<p>This time, we are looking for a kitten named Rozan with gray and black stripes. To call for its attention in cat language, you should say \"Meow meow meow, meow meow meow.\" Say it quickly with no elongation.</p>",
                "id": "Additional Information16048",
                "img": "",
                "title": "Rozan Version:"
              }
            ]
          }
        }
